"attr-right td-list-item\">PORTABLE DESIGN: Sluice Box folds down compact for easy storage and carrying. You can backpack this gold sluice box into remote areas or even carry it inside a 5 gallon bucket</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">EFFORTLESS USE: All you need to do is make sure your sluice box is level in the field. When extended in stream, the sluice box body is designed to lock rigidly in place so that it does not fold up and collapse without warning</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">HIGH-YIELD GOLD RECOVERY: 18 gauge steel zinc-plated riffles are built in throughout the sediment channel trapping gold flake and small gold nuggets in the woven vinyl miners moss which is pre-installed and ready to use out of the box</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">DURABLE CONSTRUCTION: Made to be used; designed to be portable; the backpack sluice box for gold panning is lightweight made from highly durable aluminum. It will surly withstand the harshest environments</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SLUICE BOX SPECIFICATIONS: Extended Dimensions: 50\" Length ;  Folded Dimensions: 15\" x 10\" x 6\" ; Wide-Mouth Flange: 13.25\" ; Weight: 8.4lbs ; Comes with carpet, woven vinyl miners moss and shoulder strap</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor 50\" Gold Sluice Box Folding Aluminum Gold Prospecting Equipment</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">199.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Pan for gold anywhere, anytime with the ASR Outdoor Backpack Folding Gold Sluice Box for gold prospecting. Extremely portable, folding down in size simply by loosening the connecting wing nuts, it will pack right up into your backpack. You're ready to prospect for gold right out of the package with woven vinyl miners moss included and installed.\n\nSimplify your gold prospecting and mining with the ASR Outdoor Aluminum Folding Gold Sluice Box.\n\nThis lightweight, aluminum folding sluice box incorporates traditional tried and true design aspects in an elongated 50\" run out, with a large wide mouth flare opening. What makes this unit different and extra handy is the ability to fold up to just 15 inches tall by 10 inches wide, easily fitting into a backpack or 5 gallon bucket that is ideal for all day hikers, adventurers, and seasoned miner 49ers. You can backpack this folding sluice into remote areas anywhere!\n\nThe sluice box body is designed to lock rigidly in place when the sluice is unfolded. This takes care of the most common complaint about similar cheaper models in that they would often fold up when you tried to pick them up out of the stream.\n\nThe sluice box riffles feature Uni-Body construction, the riffles are precision laser cut from a single piece of 18 gauge steel and then formed into ultra light, sturdy steel riffles. These are then zinc plated for long, rust-free service.\n\nDue to its simplicity and portability, this is a great gold recovery sluice box for beginners and serious prospecting enthusiasts alike!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n\t\t\t<p>© 2026</p></div></div><div style=\"clear:both\"><table></table>\n\t</div>\n\n <center><br></center>",
